data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath 1403 Sq.Ft home located on a corner lot. Features include a cozy gas fireplace, stainless steel appliances, pantry, and tile porcelain in kitchen and dining, with vinyl plank flooring throughout. The property offers a spacious storage shed, fenced backyard, private RV parking, and a relaxing outdoor patio all within the tranquil Lighthouse Estate community.  Check out the virtual 3D Tour. Call your local realtor to schedule a showing.
